column1: # N00: reduce-commute-times - Reduce average commute time from 45 minutes to 25 minutes
# N01: improve-air-quality - Meet EPA air quality standards year-round
# N02: affordable-transportation - Ensure low-income residents spend less than 10% of income on transportation
# N03: downtown-vitality - Create thriving downtown with easy access for customers and employees
# N04: safe-cycling-infrastructure - Protected bike lanes and trails where families feel safe cycling
# N05: transit-reliability - Transit runs on-time 95%+ with frequency under 10 minutes peak
# N06: parking-availability - Adequate parking for drivers who need it
# N07: walkable-neighborhoods - Reduce car dependency by enabling walking/biking for daily needs
# N08: cost-efficiency - Maximize mobility improvement per taxpayer dollar spent
# N09: climate-action - Reduce transportation sector carbon emissions to meet climate goals
# N10: equitable-access - Ensure all neighborhoods have equal access to jobs and services
